Key Match Events: Nikola Jokic recorded a triple-double with 35 points, 15 rebounds, and 12 assists
Damian Lillard hit a game-winning three-pointer at the buzzer
Kawhi Leonard made two clutch free throws to seal the win in overtime
Post-Match Reflections: LeBron James expressed pride in his team's effort after the comeback win
The coach highlighted the victory as a crucial step toward the championship
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Warriors led by 31 points in the first half
The Rockets tied it with an 18-2 run to open the fourth quarter
Eason led the Rockets with a career-high 27 points
Andrew Wiggins added 15 points for Golden State in his return
Jonathan Kuminga scored the first two baskets of overtime to make it 123-119
Others: The Warriors improved to 5-1 this season without Curry
Houston played much better after halftime than it did in the first half
Houston made just 1 of 12 shots in overtime
